  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Female

          -  Minimum age of 17

          -  Childhood sexual abuse

          -  Posttraumatic Stress Disorder (criteria of SCID)

          -  At least one of the following diagnoses: Anorexia Nervosa, or Bulimia Nervosa, or
             substance abuse, or substance dependence, or major depression or at least 4 out of 9
             criteria for Borderline Personality Disorder

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of schizophrenia

          -  Mental retardation

          -  Body Mass Index lower than 16.5

          -  Acute delirium

          -  Perilous selfharming behaviour during the last 4 month

          -  Suicide attempt with the distinct intention to die during the last 4 month

          -  Unstability (e.g. homelessness, acute victimisation by offender)

          -  Pretreatment by DCT
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
